Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:03:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Responding to an emergency signal,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others went to Punk \NHazard and there, they faced...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu! It's strange but it's cool here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's stuck in the dragon's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lion Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Nami and the others were...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that they're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will care if they go missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take them to the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Straw Hats Stunned! Enter: A \NSamurai's Horrifying Severed Head!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,PUNK HAZARD ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BURNING LANDS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what should we do about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pull him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your hands off of me-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm helping you! Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's completely stuck \Nin the dragon's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His upper body is stuck but \Nhe's talking normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he suffocating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's torn in half! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Sorry isn't \Nenough!  You killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm finally separated from it-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lower body just talked! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A zombie! A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no upper half here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.21,0:05:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't have an upper \Nbody from the very start?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is too freaky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind of big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is there and what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense your presence but \NI don't have eyes or ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bizarre!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are \Nbut get out of my way-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he took off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That goddamn Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Why don't you join my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you grill the dragon for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is so whimsical.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he like that monster so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It troubles me that he \Nmentioned the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean one of the Seven \NWarlords is here on this island too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! That's too much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna face the Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do it-bu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know someone's after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel any hostile intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:07:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu! I don't know who you are but \Nwhat do you want from me-bu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stand in my way, I'll fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that crap and join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bu! What are you doing-bu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, why don't you join...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my crew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey legs, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you ended up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this dragon meat is yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you call someone like this, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's called...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a centaur, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A centaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, he was stuck to the \Ndragon's body and now Luffy's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I'm stuck in something again-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's vulgar, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? He's not gonna just go along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet his upper half is looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back to his owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your sense of adventure, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was born like this. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so he's naturally a \Nhalf-body... No, I don't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know you're gonna eat most
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of this dragon meat so \Nwhy don't you carry it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Come and take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Zoro! Is the samurai \Nand the guy who got cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! S-Snowcapped mountains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, are those mountains of ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a big lake in the middle \Nand there are snowcapped
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mountains on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on this side, there is an active \Nvolcano and it's burning hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of island is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So one of the mysteries is solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh yeah, the man on \Nthe Snail said he was cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold... Is this the Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My colleagues are getting \Ncut one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai are gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means the killer samurai and \Nthe victims are on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island is so interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is snow on those mountains, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot here - I wanna eat a snowcone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna go there! It's too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's a long way. Let's \Ngo back to the ship for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it's gonna be cold this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are animals, we \Ncould make coats from pelts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not gonna be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you guys go along with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowcone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said "Wait"! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you two are going too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no immediate threat to \Nmy life here but over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll freeze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! What're you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw... I saw a monster! \NA bird! No, a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bird or a human, which was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking \Nabout? Nobody's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee! Hey, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, believe me! There was \Nsomebody just a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to report, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We seized intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume they are pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were running low on guinea pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... They all look \Nunique and interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna be good test subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:15:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I thought  you would \Nespecially like this cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a rare find!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is worth testing. You're \Nright. I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this be all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there was another man who \Nlooked like one of them but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume they had a falling \Nout and he was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remained was his skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such brutality is not so unusual for pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to lock them in a room \Nand make sure they can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what they have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for food or something usable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Nami-san and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was very hot before
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it became extremely \Ncold while I was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of those pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bone-chillingly cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm a skeleton - that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The skeletonized body said something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are but do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where Nami-san and the others went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, wait, you guys! Don't be so rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, what are you messing around with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, Franky! We are locked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this place?! Where are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was eating a Giant Shellfish \Ndessert on the deck and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember anything after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that somebody used sleeping gas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and seized us once we fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship was, in fact, filled with gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've noticed it a little sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gonna sell us?! \NAre they abducting humans?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if they took all of us \Non the ship, where's Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only four of us in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're abducting humans, \Nthey wouldn't need a skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a human either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither are you! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anybody say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys like hanjimono?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means "puzzles" in a foreign language.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it this thing that just talked?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me an "it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new kind of Transponder Snail?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are eight of them! I hadn't noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't seem like bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all parts of my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask you to put them back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, this is a mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How is it?!\N--Yeah, looks like a face now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, you left out some parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, this is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna try it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Stop playing with my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a human face now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there is something \Nwrong with the chin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the top part but it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A severed-head just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you live like \Nthat?! Are you possessed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I didn't \Nwish to become like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard... He used \Nsome kind of weird magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was dead when he cut \Nme but I ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be kept alive after \Nbeing sliced apart is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a dishonor to a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like crossing the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the only way to get to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how do we cross the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if we can live long enough \Nto get to the lake in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowcone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Luffy can be so high-spirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowcone! Snowcone! Snowcone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.43,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for intruders and \NI saw some unfamiliar faces so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay! You surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, your legs are cool too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Your hind legs are a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I-bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hind legs can talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! None of my friends \Nhave legs like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I've never seen it before!\N--Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Luffy made an odd friend again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A panther centaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...three...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and four.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we found them. We \Nwere about to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.09,0:22:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are four intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:22:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the crew face a new crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while they cross the burning lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Sanji and the others hear what \Nthe bodiless samurai has to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they escape together from their cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While being pursued, they wander into a room,
